 as household (features/ qualities/ traits). The profit function in Eq. (1) is 
 composed of two parts/pieces: the (capable of being seen and known) part V and 
 an error term Îµ. The error term is unknown to the (person who works to find information), but 
 may be known to the farmer. The farmer will choose the animals that gives him the highest (money made/good thing received). The farmer will choose 
